ears cut commission rates for employees in select departments to anywhere from  to  but equalized the base wage across all home improvement and electronics departments in  commission rates on nonbase items were cut by  in the electronics department in late  the commission on sales of base items from the electronic department was cut to  as of  appliances is the only remaining department where compensation is based entirely on commission other departments give a base pay plus commission in many stores jewelry department associates receive a low base salary with  commission on their sales galleryedit letterhead logo  logo – – – still used in mexico and puerto rico – – in canada –present exterior of the sears at the westfield hawthorn in vernon hills illinois mall entrance to the sears at plaza del norte in hatillo puerto rico mall entrance to the sears at paramus park in paramus new jersey exterior of the sears essentials in west palm beach florida reopened as sears outlet  photo of the mall entrance to the sears grand at pittsburgh mills in tarentum pennsylvania this sears closed in january  exterior of the sears parts  repair store in brooklyn ohio exterior of the sears in mexico city see alsoedit chicago portal illinois portal companies portal sears canada – canadian unit sears mexico – mexican unit held by grupo carso sears plc – former uk company unrelated to us retailer referencesedit  sears holdings first quarter  earnings release sears holdings retrieved may     a b sears holdings corporation   form k sears holding corporation pdf report united states securities and exchange commission p  retrieved december      sales lift walmart into top spot sun sentinel february   retrieved january     gelles david october   for oncemighty sears pictures of decay the new york times   correctedupdate sears turns to lampert again for cash before holiday season reuters retrieved october      top  retailers storesorg retrieved january     clymer floyd treasury of early america