 obligations to process my claim as quickly as possible how do i know what accessories i will need to send in with my product can i purchase the sears purchaseprotect plan to cover merchandise that i have already purchased how can i contact customer service you can get immediate help during call center hours by calling  or you can access our online customer service help by clicking here  back to top  my claim is not coming up on your web page what should i do if you have a valid salescheck showing your purchase of the sears purchaseprotect agreement our customer service center can verify it for you please call for assistance at   back to top  how long does it take to get my claim fulfilled the process time varies depending on your product and whether or not you need to process a return shipment to our returns center it can take anywhere from    business days to process your claim if you have a specific question about your claim please call customer service at   back to top  how do i process a claim within the store return policy  or  days as shown on your receipt a retain your original sales receipt as proof of purchase return to the sears store where you purchased your product to take advantage of sears store return policy after expiration of the store return policy  or  days as shown on your receipt a do not return the defective product to the store returns may be made at the store only within the time frame indicated on your receipt unless you are exercising your product manufacturer’s warranty and the product information directs you back to the sears store you should follow the directions for making a claim in your sears purchaseprotect contract b log on to wwwsearspurchaseprotectcom to initiate your claim or register your plan if you do not have access to a computer or prefer calling call  a customer service associate will walk you through the process and can initiate the claim for you c have your original sales receipt and purchase date this will be required to make a claim d well confirm your product defect and verify your address you will have the opportunity to download a prepaid shipping label or have one mailed to you its important to note that products with no defect found or accidental damage will be returned and in that case gift card may not be issued please see terms and conditions for complete details e once you have the prepaid shipping label ship the defective product or component to our returns processing center use the original product box and packing material if you have them they are designed specifically for the transfer of your product to expedite the process please include all accessories that came with your original purchase including the owners manual before sending your product to our returns center click here to view the list of common accessories f youll receive a gift card for the original purchase price including sales tax by return mail if you purchase your replacement in advance and can show proof of that purchase at your sears store by receipt number and purchase date you will receive an option to receive a check rather than a gift card in some cases sears reserves the right to ship a refurbished replacement for certain products that may not be in stock at your local sears stores g use the gift card to replace your defective product with a replacement product of your choice at any sears store nationwide h you are responsible for any difference between the purchase price of your selected replacement and the gift card any excess funds will be placed on a sears gift card  back to top  will my existing plan cover the new replacement product purchased no the plan is designed for a onetime use and the contract is fulfilled after the gift card is issued thats why the price is so low if you use the gift card to replace the defective product with a replacement product of your choice we recommend you purchase a new sears purchaseprotect plan  back to top  does the sears purchaseprotect plan replace my manufacturers coverage no it provides a more simplified alternative to the manufacturers coverage most standard warranties do not provide replacement coverage in addition they often require you to ship it in for repair at your expense your spp contract provides an advantage to replace your product in a flexible way you are free to contact the manufacturer during their coverage period if you would rather reserve your onetime gift card replacement option for a later date within the term to contact your manufacturer please go to their web site or call them at the number listed in your owner’s manual  back to top  what are my obligations to process my claim as quickly as possible your original sales transaction showing your sears purchaseprotect is the most important piece of our claims process because it proves your purchase and coverage it also speeds verification to expedite the process please include all accessories that accompanied your original purchase including owners manual before sending your product to our product testing centerclick here to view the list of accessories which may have accompanied your product during your original purchase click here to view the list of common accessories  back to top  how do i know what accessories i will need to send in with my product click here to view the list of common accessories which may have come with your product during your original purchase  back to top  can i purchase the sears purchaseprotect plan to cover merchandise that i have already purchased the sears purchaseprotect plan must be purchased on select eligible merchandise at the same time as the purchase of the merchandise to be covered at a sears store or on searscom the sears purchaseprotect plan cannot be purchased to cover previously purchased merchandise  back to top  help  terms  conditions  troubleshooting product failure  product recalls  shop searscom   sears brand llc  sears product information network  intro  spin spin ready to spin enter here   