ates levels of neurotoxic betaamyloid in the brain cancernovel targets that modulate p stability increasing tumorcell sensitivity to cytotoxic and radiation therapiesthey believe its intellectual property and scientific rationale for future compound discovery offers a compelling opportunity for commercializationsmart is led by management and scientific advisory teams comprised of preeminent professionals distinguished in the worlds of academic science pharmaceutical discovery businesscorporate development finance and intellectual property law the smart biosciences leadership team brings scientific rigor business leadership and innovation experience to its endeavorsits discovery and development strategy employs a uniquetotheindustry collaborative network of advanced business academic and rd interests throughout the united states and asia director prior vybion inc vybion inc develops human monoclonal antibody drugs it offers recombinant proteins including biotherapeutics viral antigens cellular proteins cytokines and other proteins for diagnostic therapeutic and reagent applications the company was founded by lee a henderson in  and is headquartered in ithaca ny political donations   joe hoeffel former representative from pennsylvanias th congressional district   al gore jr former vice president at office of the vice president under bill clinton   joe hoeffel former representative from pennsylvanias th congressional district   democratic congressional campaign committee the democratic congressional campaign committee dccc is the official campaign arm of the democrats in the house the dccc is the only political committee in the country whose principal mission is to support democratic house candidates every step of the way   william j clinton former president of united states see  more listings with relsci professional start my free trial ➤ see  more other affiliations peter a sears is affiliated with quaker partners management lp sr one ltd glaxosmithkline plc protez p